org.cpsolver.studentsct.online.selection

Class SuggestionsBranchAndBound

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.cpsolver.studentsct.online.selection.SuggestionsBranchAndBound
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    MultiCriteriaBranchAndBoundSuggestions

    public class SuggestionsBranchAndBound
extends Object
    Computation of suggestions using a limited depth branch and bound. For a given schedule and a selected section, compute possible changes that will be displayed to the student as suggestions. The number of suggestions is limited by Suggestions.MaxSuggestions parameter (defaults to 20). Time is limited by Suggestions.Timeout (defaults to 5000 ms), search depth is limited by Suggestions.MaxDepth parameter (default to 4).
    Version:
    StudentSct 1.3 (Student Sectioning)
